19 Sarve ete pūrṇāḥ santi durātmabhiḥ;
20 yataḥ punar api tava paryāpnoti kevalam darśanam,
21 jānīhi katham ca kena ca ete niyamitāḥ santi.

28 Himsrakānāṃ prathamo maṇḍalaḥ sarvaḥ;
29 Tatra ca tribhyaḥ puruṣebhyaḥ balāt kāryamāṇatvāt,
30 Triṣu paridhiṣu vibhaktaḥ saṃracitaca asti.

34 Mṛtyur balātkṛtaḥ tathā piḍājanakāḥ kṣatayaḥ
35 Sahakāriṣu dīyante, tathā tasya vastuni
36 Vināśāḥ dagdhāḥ harṣaṇāni ca hānikarāṇi;

46 Devatāyām balam kartum śakyate,
47 hṛdayena naṣṭakṛtvā tām nindanīyakṛtya ca,
48 prakṛtim tasyāḥ śubhatām ca avajñāyitum;

55 Ayaṃ pratinivṛtter mārgaḥ chinatti
56 svabhāvajam sneham api;
57 atas tvadvitiye maṇḍale niṣīdanti

61 Anyatra mārgeṇa saḥ premaḥ viśṛtaḥ
62 yaḥ prakṛtiḥ karoti, yaśca tataḥ anuyojitaḥ,
63 yataḥ viśeṣaḥ śraddhāḥ sambhūtā;

100 daivīyāt buddher api ca tasya kalayā;
101 ca yadi tvam tava Vaiśeṣikam jānāsi,
102 tvam prāpsyasi, na bahuṣu patreṣu,

103 yathāśakti yathā śiṣyaḥ guruṃ,
104 tathā yūyam anukarotha prakṛtim;
105 tasmāt yūyaṃ Deva-pautra iva."

